Class AbstractMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
ie.ucd.csnl.comp47500.impl.AbstractMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:

V - the type of mapped values
All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<K,V>, Iterable<Entry<K,V>>
Direct Known Subclasses:
HashMapImpl
public abstract class AbstractMap<K,V> extends Object implements Map<K,V>
An abstract class that provides a skeletal implementation of the Map interface. This class provides common functionality and default implementations for various methods. Subclasses of AbstractMap must implement the abstract methods to provide concrete implementations of the Map interface.
